### Check-In API (Phase 1)
@reservationId = e47ab7b2-90be-4a30-a33f-68f35c6ee476
@eventDate = 2026-02-14
### 1) Get active pass (read-only; does NOT issue a new pass)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reservations/{{reservationId}}/check-in-pass?eventDate={{eventDate}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 2) Issue first pass (or reuse current active pass if already issued)
POST {{baseUrl}}/reservations/{{reservationId}}/check-in-pass
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventDate": "{{eventDate}}",
  "reissue": false
}

### 3) Force reissue pass (revokes previous active pass)
POST {{baseUrl}}/reservations/{{reservationId}}/check-in-pass
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventDate": "{{eventDate}}",
  "reissue": true
}

### 4) Verify/consume pass token (one-time use)
### Can send raw token, qr payload, or full URL containing ?token=

POST {{baseUrl}}/check-in/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "a574bb4205ae4c40aee1a7eeb2751609d0b81094a5b343fd8e776da586b3861e",
  "scannerDevice": "door-ipad-1"
}
